ubation times can be adjusted but the reaction efficiency may\u00a0decrease.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":null,"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":null},{"id":718480,"guid":"C7187CE696E54B8F8912F2AA10E2082F","previous_id":718479,"previous_guid":"8CBB8AB22FBB45CD991C7D8C70D81DA4","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"45AF1F90EF8C400D9920923375AA95E0","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Transform and plate"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"F4050450247E416DB86073374DFBAB34","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Use 1\u00a0\u00b5L of reaction to transform chemically competent cells.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Recover in SOC for 1 hour incubating at 37 \u00baC in a shaking incubator.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Prepare plates with respective antibiotics with 50 ug\/mL of X-GAL and 1 mM IPTG.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":null,"data":null,"section":null,"section_color":null},{"id":718481,"guid":"2A67BAA3FD544FBF88D5EC91CE0B4B39","previous_id":718480,"previous_guid":"C7187CE696E54B8F8912F2AA10E2082F","modified_on":0,"protocol_id":0,"components":[{"id":1054723,"guid":"EEF5C7D3B0494ACB817AB9F9552FC1CD","order_id":1,"type_id":6,"title":"Section","source":{"title":"Pick colony grow overnight and validate"}},{"id":1054724,"guid":"F4AE7C0C42C14064A558A590C438F140","order_id":1,"type_id":1,"title":"description","source":{"description":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Pick 2 white colonies for each construction and grow in\u00a010 mL of LB + respective antibiotic and perform plasmid purification. Validate assembly by means of restriction digest. Suggested enzymes: ThermoFischer XbaI and PstI FastDigest enzymes. If higher concentrations are required, increase inoculation volume and perform Midi prep as directed by manufacturer's instructions.<\/div><\/div>"}}],"cases":null,"data":null,"section":null,"section_